title: Cisco ASA, ASDM, AnyConnect, ent, CDA, ASAv, SecurityPlus.
description:
Warning 0: Only for learning. Don't for production use.
Description of directories:
5500 - Software on chassis for cisco asa 5500 series
5500-x - Software on chassis for cisco asa 5500-X series
5505 - Software on chassis for cisco asa 5505 only
ASDM - Adaptive Security Appliance Device Manager
AnyConnect - Cisco AnyConnect Secure Mobility Client (web-vpn technology)
CDA - Context Directory Agent
ASAv and 1000V - ASA operating system for VMware vSphere (ova (all in one) files)
AD Agent - AD Agent
Doc - link to documentation
Cisco ASA 5540 8.2(1) Keymaker v1.0 (Sep 2009) by SSG - SecurityPlus Keymaker
1. In "Cisco ASA 5540 8.2(1) Keymaker v1.0 (Sep 2009) by SSG.exe" press "Greedy" button.
2. Run "show version" via console or ssh and copy serial number to first field of keymaker.
3. Use maximum numbers from guide http://www.cisco.com/c/en/us/td/docs/security/asa/asa84/license/license_management/license.html (table for you platform).
4. Press "Etis atis animatis" button, copy activation key in you device, reboot device.
Warning 1: If you need feature set more than keymaker include, then be careful: unknown function will be off.
Warning 2: Only for learning. Don't for production use.
Information must be free
Best regards, anonymouse
